	<!-- Text  -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Cold Front</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_HELP">
			<Text>Noble leader, I bring you troubling news. The winters near our City have grown harsher of late, and our people who keep track of these things predict a particularly cold snap is on its way.[NEWLINE]We have some ideas, Your Wonderousness. How should we deal with this issue?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The City generates {3_CityYield} for {5_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>The storm pillages up to one of each: Farm, Lumbermill, Mine, and Quarry. Receive a free Worker.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Villages and Towns generate +1 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production but lose -1 [ICON_FOOD] Food for {5_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Villages and Towns generate +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and +2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold but lose -2 [ICON_FOOD] Food for {5_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_HELP_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Every [ICON_GREAT_ENGINEER] Engineer in the City generates +2 [ICON_FOOD] Food, at the cost of {3_CityYield} in the City, all for {5_Turns}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>People are ice-skating on the River for the first time in living memory. How quaint. Are these extensive contingencies really necessary?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>I'm very concerned by the weather system's interaction with the freezing ocean. This is worse than any of you thought. We need Workers here to brace ourselves against the coming storm.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>The Science Advisor's scheme whereby our local stockpile of Salt could be used to secure some of our low-level infrastructure from this inclement weather is an elegant solution. Impliment that!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>These are excellent plans. With our Promethean ability to generate heat, we should be able to warm every home in three Tiles for the whole winter!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_COLD_FRONT_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>So you are telling me that with our expertise in plumbing and manufacturing that we can fit every home with a central heating system? Get on that immediately!</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
